-| Edge Case | Handling | Verification |
-|-----------|----------|--------------|
-| Empty arguments | Uses all defaults | Γ£à Tested |
-| Numeric string as RepoPath | Treated as MaxDepth if not found | Γ£à Tested (backward compat) |
-| Path with spaces | Properly quoted in command | Γ£à Supported |
-| Relative path | Resolved to absolute | Γ£à Tested |
-| UNC path | Supported and processed | Γ£à Supported |
-| Non-existent path | Clear error message | Γ£à Tested |
-| Forward slashes in path | Detected correctly | Γ£à Supported |
-| Trailing backslash in path | Handled gracefully | Γ£à Supported |
