+
+---
+
+## ≡ƒöä Flow Comparison
+
+### OLD PATTERN (Single Flow)
+```
+VoidAuthFlow
+Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ Derives from authVoid.authVoid_With_All_Fields
+Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ Pre-populated with auth context
+ΓööΓöÇΓöÇ Direct void processing
+```
+
+### NEW PATTERN (Two Transactions)
+```
+AuthFlow (cached in flowMap)
+Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ Derives from authFPAN.newAuth
+Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ Uses getElavonAuthBaseInteraction()
+ΓööΓöÇΓöÇ Response fields extracted
+
+VoidFlow (depends on AuthFlow)
+Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ Derives from authVoid.authVoid_With_All_Fields
+Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ Calls applyAssociateFields()
+Γöé   ΓööΓöÇΓöÇ Maps auth response ΓåÆ void request
+Γö£ΓöÇΓöÇ Uses getElavonVoidBaseInteraction()
+ΓööΓöÇΓöÇ Applies scenario customizations
+```
