+## ≡ƒÄ» Key Features Implemented
+
+### Two-Transaction Pattern
+```
+1. Base Auth Transaction (createAuthFlowForVoidScenario)
+   Γö£ΓöÇ Derives from authFPAN.newAuth
+   Γö£ΓöÇ Uses getElavonAuthBaseInteraction()
+   ΓööΓöÇ Cached in flowMap for later reference
+
+2. Void Auth Transaction (createVoidFlowForScenario)
+   Γö£ΓöÇ Derives from authVoid.authVoid_With_All_Fields
+   Γö£ΓöÇ Uses getElavonVoidBaseInteraction()
+   ΓööΓöÇ Calls applyAssociateFields() for field mapping
+```
+
+### Safe Field Mapping (applyAssociateFields)
+- Γ£à Null-check: Verify auth flow exists
+- Γ£à Safe copy: Use copyFieldFromDependency()
+- Γ£à Exception handling: Try-catch with logging
+- Γ£à Graceful degradation: Continue on missing fields
+
