+## ≡ƒÄô KEY IMPLEMENTATION PATTERNS
+
+### Pattern 1: Two-Transaction with Field Mapping
+```java
+// Step 1: Create and cache base auth
+authFlows = VoidScenarios.values()
+    .map(this::createAuthFlowForVoidScenario)
+
+// Step 2: Create void with dependent mapping
+voidFlows = VoidScenarios.values()
+    .map(this::createVoidFlowForScenario)
+    
+// Step 3: Combine
+members(flatten(Stream.concat(authFlows, voidFlows)))
+```
+
+### Pattern 2: Safe Field Mapping
+```java
+// Layer 1: Null-check
+Flow authFlow = flowMap.get(scenario);
+if (authFlow == null) {
+    log warning + return;
+}
+
+// Layer 2: Safe copy + Layer 3: Exception handling
+try {
+    copyFieldFromDependency(...).accept(voidFlow);
+} catch (Exception e) {
+    log warning + continue; // non-blocking
+}
+```
